做鳩死，車迷當睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你做manager ，成班細既反你，你完全冇責任既</blockquote><br />\n咩責任？班車仔球員咁鬼衰，你班車迷都話專程飛過去睇車仔波，但班球星睬都唔睬下你地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"975154a69725dfb372e1745f450e066927efd3e1","tid":351324,"uid":51951,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T05:03:27.000Z","msg":"摩帶車拎3個英超（好似係三個），即管睇下干地幫車拎到幾多個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea911d53936f19248b54969456ef9d7653b36f9b","tid":351324,"uid":45917,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T05:11:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>明明摩佬係俾班球員同隊醫做鳩死，車迷當睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你做manager ，成班細既反你，你完全冇責任既</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咁差<br />\nmatic lukaku唔會返番去佢身邊啦<br />\n發生咩事<br />\n心照啦"},{"pid":"a3f23fbef68f43bc8e26a359414ae6d91359de64","tid":351324,"uid":35820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T05:17:26.000Z","msg":"盧卡古 迪布尼個時走都好正常<br />\n想踢正選又未夠班<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3822443d3b06da88158d9f3eaef001124f6bb2db","tid":351324,"uid":34562,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T05:23:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>盧卡古 迪布尼個時走都好正常<br />\n想踢正選又未夠班<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n普巴咪一樣俾廢sir免費放走，但佢地剩係識笑鳩曼聯俾咁多錢買返黎，但個班球員唔走，留係車仔撚有機會變到咁勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n普巴冇派路同維度係身邊，邊有今日咁勁，班友都忽忽地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed4b21e82656a4b5896d2247be333643855da499","tid":351324,"uid":22024,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T05:29:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>明明摩佬係俾班球員同隊醫做鳩死，車迷當睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你做manager ，成班細既反你，你完全冇責任既</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咁差<br />\nmatic lukaku唔會返番去佢身邊啦<br />\n發生咩事<br />\n心照啦</blockquote><br />\n正解<br />\n根本好多人感激摩佬<br />\nLKK係感激摩佬肯比佢走<br />\n相反迪布尼仲屌緊<br />\n講真，唔比你走都無咁多機會落場去進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec3b9b39043f7f5ae2baa4446677ca1c428adb0","tid":351324,"uid":4586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T05:29:46.000Z","msg":"叫你老鼠真係無錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當年反摩 而家走左就反干<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78dc8d53ac8b39a1ce0aa9727039f711b683736e","tid":351324,"uid":45917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T05:38:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叫你老鼠真係無錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當年反摩 而家走左就反干<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我無反個摩<br />\n係唔撚知邊個話我係 老鼠<br />\n我完全唔識"},{"pid":"40c983ccfae9d2ad747390c0fc651fa2877fd55f","tid":351324,"uid":18271,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T05:42:23.000Z","msg":"有盃嗰時叫daddy<br />\n無嗰時叫摩狗<br />\n自己球員迫害領隊當睇唔到嚟<br />\n新領隊嚟列有英超冠軍就話摩佬教到護級無料到<br />\n真係唔知有幾低賤先做得出屌球會英雄呢d行為<br />\n捧得車仔人格都有d問題"},{"pid":"746e5f7354d62489afe55de7cadc213b29fdb7a0","tid":351324,"uid":51951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T05:48:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每隔一年就見到轟迷鬧爆領隊<br />\n一年串咀一年潛水一年串咀一年潛水</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"789daa6e74ba421f9d4a95fdee209f2eb5b23635","tid":351324,"uid":45917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T05:48:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有盃嗰時叫daddy<br />\n無嗰時叫摩狗<br />\n自己球員迫害領隊當睇唔到嚟<br />\n新領隊嚟列有英超冠軍就話摩佬教到護級無料到<br />\n真係唔知有幾低賤先做得出屌球會英雄呢d行為<br />\n捧得車仔人格都有d問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我一直叫daddy<br />\n唔好搞錯<br />\n我係撐摩俾人叫到要闌 離開車區"},{"pid":"499f75480269df4cc191014f4dfbd3d7e4a4fae2","tid":